<h2>Presentations from Meetings</h2>

<p>

The presentations from the WG meeting in San Diego (December 2000) are:
<ul>
<li><a href="ietf49-requirements.ppt">Requirements document</a>
<li><a href="ietf49-dhcp.ppt">DHCP configuration</a>
<li><a href="ietf49-GetCert.ppt">GetCert protocol</a>
<li><a href="ietf49-PIC.ppt">PIC protocol</a>
</ul>

<p>The presentations from the WG meeting in Pittsburgh (July 2000) are:
<ul>
<li><a href="ietf48-requirements.ppt">Scott Kelly on the requirements
document</a> (PowerPoint)
<li><a href="ietf48-dhcp.ppt">Bernard Aboba on the DHCP configuration
document</a> (PowerPoint)
</ul>

<p>Presentations from the WG meeting in Adelaide (March 2000) include:
<ul>
<li><a href="ietf47-Bellovin.ps">Steve Bellovin on getcert</a> (PostScript)
<li><a href="ietf47-Sheffer.ppt">Yaron Sheffer on PIC</a> (PowerPoint)
<li><a href="ietf47-Srisuresh.ppt">Pyda Srisuresh on configuration</a> (PowerPoint)
<li><a href="ietf47-ULA.ppt">Scott Kelly on authentication</a> (PowerPoint)
<li><a href="ietf47-dhcp.ppt">Scott Kelly on configuration with DHCP</a> (PowerPoint)
</ul>

<p>
The PowerPoint <a href="ietf46-ipsra.ppt">BOF agenda for Washington (November
1999)</a> is available.


